text.section:
The patent shall contain:
The name of the person to whom it is issued;
The name given to the land;
The name of the original applicant;
The date of issuance of the warrant;
The name of any person substituted as applicant and the date of the substitution;
The date of filing the certificate or amended certificate of survey on which the patent is based;
A description of the land, as contained in the certificate of survey; and
The Commissioner's certificate that the patent is proper to be issued.
